title: Did Kanye West Receive 60K Votes for US President?
subtitle: West conceded his presidential bid on Election Day, but it may not be the last time we see him on the ballot.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: A Facebook post sharing screenshots of state-by-state vote counts taken on Nov. 4, 2020, showed rapper Kanye West as having garnered tens of thousands of presidential votes in the general election.
